<h2> Definition </h2>

<p>
<strong>@HI{{deshou}}</strong> expresses the speaker's conjecture, possibly from some information he has.
</p>

<p>
When used with a rising intonation, it is being used by the speaker to confirm the listener's agreement.
</p>

